<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien pakna lunggil ka deih,
 Gitloh umlo lunggil;

[V2]
 Kei dinga luong thisan hezing ,
 Zie lunggil chu ka deih. (3) DS

[V3]
 2. Kingainiem. kipumpiek lunggil,
 Tanpa lopi ma ah;

[V4]
 Krista maiin vai A hawmna
 Ka lungsung lalchutphah. (3) DS

[V5]
 3. Lungheia, kingainiem lunggil,
 Thutak ginna thiengtho;

[V6]
 Thihnan a khen theih ngei takloh ,
 Tu-a lungsunga um, (3) DS

[V7]
 4. Bangchenga thak zosa lunggil,
 Hehpih thiengtho a dim,

[V8]
 A pha, thiengtho leh dik bukim,
 Keile ei neihsak in. (3) DS

[V9]
 5. Nangmah hindan thiengtho ei pien,
 Chunglam akipat in,

[V10]
 Ka lung sungah ei ziksak in,
 Nei hehpina Min lul. (3) DS</lyrics>
<title>Pahchakna Lunggil</title>
<hymn_number>147</hymn_number>
</song>